   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Valerius		33 arouras
Aion son of Sarapion	28 arouras
Heras			2 1/2 1/8 arouras
Tapaeis		12 1/2 arouras
Heirs of Aleia and Tamaleis	5 2/3 arouras
Total			81 2/3 1/8 arouras

... Aion through Isidoros	- talents
The same, another		20,000 talents
Aion				3,000 talents
... Aion			1,000 talents

</ab>
